sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as ds-pipeline-api-server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant ArgoCtrl as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Launcher as Pipeline Pod<br/>(launcher/driver)
    participant MLMD as ds-pipeline-metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>9000 or 443/TCP

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBP: TLS Reencrypt
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(DSPA subresource 'api')
    KRBP->>API: Forward (HTTP/HTTPS)<br/>PodToPodTLS when enabled
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>TLS (configurable), Password auth
    API->>S3: Store pipeline spec artifact<br/>TLS (configurable), AccessKey/SecretKey
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount token
    ArgoCtrl->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount token
    ArgoCtrl->>K8s: Create Pipeline Pods<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount token
    Launcher->>MLMD: Log execution metadata<br/>gRPC, mTLS (PodToPodTLS)
    Launcher->>S3: Upload/download artifacts<br/>HTTPS, AccessKey/SecretKey
    Launcher->>API: Report step status<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, PodToPodTLS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: MLMD Lineage Query (Dashboard)

    participant MDRoute as OpenShift Route (MLMD)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBPmd as kube-rbac-proxy (Envoy)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP

    User->>MDRoute: GET lineage data<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MDRoute->>KRBPmd: TLS Reencrypt
    KRBPmd->>KRBPmd: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBPmd->>Envoy: Forward (plaintext localhost)
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC request<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Query lineage<br/>MySQL, TLS, Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage records
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
    Envoy-->>KRBPmd: Response
    KRBPmd-->>MDRoute: HTTPS response
    MDRoute-->>User: JSON/gRPC response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Managed Pipelines Import

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    DSPO->>OCI: Fetch managed-pipelines.json<br/>HTTPS, Registry credentials
    OCI-->>DSPO: Pipeline manifest
    DSPO->>DSPO: Validate pipeline names<br/>(block on invalid, warn on transient)
    Note over DSPO: Init container extracts<br/>pipelines from OCI image<br/>into shared volume
    API->>API: Import from /config/managed-pipelines/
